text_logic_form: The point $S$ is the midpoint of one of the legs of the trapezoid $ABCD$.
The point $T$ is the midpoint of the other leg of the trapezoid $ABCD$.

The length of the line $CD$ is $3x + 2$.

Find the length of the line $AB$.
